    <article>
        <p>Obama signed the NDAA today.</p>
<p>The Act legislatively codifies the President&#39;s authority to indefinitely detain terrorism <em>suspects</em> without trial. This can include US citizens on American soil.</p>
<p>(at this point I had about a dozen sarcastic remarks about Obama, but really I think none are needed.)</p>

